creator: TRS Healthcare Group
descriptionHtml:
TRS Healthcare has developed the ultimate tool to enable you to have a true and real-time partnership with your recruiter to manage all aspects of your travel career with us. No longer will you have to juggle text messages and emails or play phone tag with your Recruiter to get updates or information. With TRS Nurse, you will have all the resources on hand to efficiently communicate with your recruiter and to address any requirements that come up along the way.

Have you ever had a situation where your timesheet was not received by your company? With TRS Nurse, you can submit it online. Need a copy of an old timesheet? Access and view any timesheet from your current contract.

TRS Nurse allows you to partner with your recruiter for strategizing your next assignment. Get instant alerts when you have been submitted or when you have an offer. Ask questions and provide feedback on your offers in real-time.

TRS Nurse makes the referral process simple by allowing you to refer them through your phone and keep track of every nurse you send our way. You will know if they have accepted a position and you will be notified about your earnings along the way. TRS Nurse will also let you know when your next contract will need to start to maximize your earning potential with us.

Use TRS Nurse to instantly text or call your recruiter at any time. Ask questions, provide feedback and accept a position when it’s convenient for you to do so. TRS Nurse puts you in the driver’s seat with your recruiter to manage your assignments and provide instantaneous communication.

TRS Nurse is the first app of its kind and provides user-friendly access to all TRS information, real-time interaction with relevant departments and gives you a peek behind the curtain of your travel company. TRS Healthcare invites you to the future of travel healthcare management with our cutting-edge innovation, the TRS Nurse app.

Features include:

- One-button Recruiter text and calling
- Notifications with timely & relevant messages, alerts, and reminders
- Real-time profile submission listings
- Offer & facility details
- Timesheet submission & access
- Referral management & tracking
